biography: Tommy, a formidable presence hailing from Espoo Ringside Golf, is known for his meticulous approach to the game and his unwavering dedication to improvement. While he maintains a stoic demeanor on the course, those closest to him know him as a jovial companion with a penchant for elaborate pranks.

Tommy has participated in the Hector Trophée twice. Although victory has eluded him thus far, his consistent performance demonstrates a trajectory towards success. With an unyielding spirit, Tommy is poised to make a significant impact in future tournaments.
The upcoming Hector Trophée 2025 will mark Tommy's third appearance in the competition, where he will undoubtedly bring his trademark blend of skill and determination to the course.
